  "detailed_description": "<h1>FIND HMUR!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.poster.avif?t=1765024409\" width=1170 height=426 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.webm?t=1765024409\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440850/extras/b009372be95605a3fb4580f8fe3b1d8f.mp4?t=1765024409\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1440850/extras/f231bec78cc2672914feac8f2fef6eda.avif?t=1765024409\" width=610 height=210 /></span><br><br>In the game you have to rotate the level and guide the Panda to collect coins.<br>The main character is Panda.<br>The panda is very curious and courageous in his supercocon he is able to withstand falls from great heights and can travel enormous distances.<br>You have to rotate the level, solve puzzles and, of course, collect coins. <br><br>Game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Level Rotation Adventure<br></li><li>Collecting coins<br></li><li>Convenient management<br></li><li>Difficult levels<br></li><li>Physics, doors, keys and traps.</li></ul>",
